245
00:18:01,028 --> 00:18:02,428
Apertar o botão...

246
00:18:04,894 --> 00:18:06,634
Encontrar o saco...

247
00:18:11,628 --> 00:18:13,828
E vai me encontrar
nos fundos do acampamento.

248
00:18:16,128 --> 00:18:17,528
<i>Eu terei outro emprego</i>

249
00:18:17,861 --> 00:18:19,261
